    {
      "id": "69e04efc91aa7e842196ad32",
      "text": "LLM Wiki",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1776307966,
      "updated": 1776307966
    },
    {
      "id": "69e04efd0000000000b39a2d",
      "text": "最初は、Xに投稿されたアイデア",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1776307966,
      "updated": 1776307985
    },
    {
      "id": "69e04f110000000000b39a2f",
      "text": "https://x.com/karpathy/status/2039805659525644595",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1776307985,
      "updated": 1776307986
    },
    {
      "id": "69e04f120000000000b39a30",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1776307986,
      "updated": 1776307986
    },
    {
      "id": "69e04f130000000000b39a31",
      "text": "これが話題になって、gistにアイデアノートが投稿された",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1776307987,
      "updated": 1776308000
    },
    {
      "id": "69e04f200000000000b39a32",
      "text": "https://gist.github.com/karpathy/442a6bf555914893e9891c11519de94f",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1776308000,
      "updated": 1776308006
    },
    {
      "id": "69e04f0d0000000000b39a2e",
      "text": ">A pattern for building personal knowledge bases using LLMs.",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1776307981,
      "updated": 1776308079
    },
    {
      "id": "69e04f710000000000b39a36",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1776308081,
      "updated": 1776308081
    },
    {
      "id": "69e050e10000000000a44e46",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1776308449,
      "updated": 1776308449
    },
    {
      "id": "69e050070000000000a44e41",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1776308232,
      "updated": 1776308232
    },
    {
      "id": "69e04f740000000000b39a37",
      "text": "[taktamur.icon]",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1776308084,
      "updated": 1776308232
    },
    {
      "id": "69e04f760000000000b39a39",
      "text": " 多分井戸端でお試ししてる人がいたのを見かけたような気がする",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1776308086,
      "updated": 1776308228
    },
    {
      "id": "69e050e40000000000a44e47",
      "text": " \t[AIを使った知識マネジメント] これだ",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1776308453,
      "updated": 1776308459
    },
    {
      "id": "69e050010000000000a44e3e",
      "text": " アイデアノートをLLMにつっこんで、システムをLLMに作ってもらうというのは新しいと思う",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1776308226,
      "updated": 1776308283
    },
    {
      "id": "69e050250000000000b39a3d",
      "text": " 今ある既存のobsidianのvaultに突っ込んで見たら、wikiというよりリンク集っぽくなった",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1776308261,
      "updated": 1776308261
    },
    {
      "id": "69e050010000000000a44e3f",
      "text": "  既存に似たようなページがあって、それに引っ張られた感じ",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1776308226,
      "updated": 1776308229
    },
    {
      "id": "69e050010000000000a44e40",
      "text": "  これはこれで便利なので残す",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1776308226,
      "updated": 1776308230
    },
    {
      "id": "69e04f750000000000b39a38",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1776308085,
      "updated": 1776308085
    },
    {
      "id": "69e050ac0000000000a44e45",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1776308397,
      "updated": 1776308397
    },
    {
      "id": "69e050660000000000a44e42",
      "text": "井戸端での関連しそうな記事",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1776308326,
      "updated": 1776308394
    },
    {
      "id": "69e050ee0000000000a44e48",
      "text": " [AIを使った知識マネジメント]",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1776308463,
      "updated": 1776308468
    },
    {
      "id": "69e050690000000000a44e43",
      "text": " [LLMに好きにWikiを書いてもらう遊び]",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1776308330,
      "updated": 1776308340
    },
    {
      "id": "69e0508b0000000000a44e44",
      "text": " [チャットのログからLLMでWikiのようなデータを作る]",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1776308364,
      "updated": 1776308376
    },
